CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1951, pg. 2, reads: "Leaders Attend Dinner - Dr. Grace Loucks Elliott, executive director of the National YWCA, New York, addressed a group of church and community leaders in East Liberty 'Y.' The dinner meeting climaxed a two-day institute... Right photo: Leaders of the institute, left to right: Mrs. Howard Wilburt, chairman; Mrs. Elliott, Mrs. James C. Rea, presiding officer, and Mrs. George West, president. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Mrs. Howard Wilburt, Dr. Grace Loucks Elliott, Mrs. James C. Rea, and Mrs. George West, posed behind banquet table in East Liberty YWCA
